INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (395, 2, '2009-08-12 16:00:00', '2009-08-12 14:00:00', 'Something special this week. Here\'s a couple of pictures of 2 posters I made last Monday, as part of a <a href="http://ingliveart.blogspot.com" target="_blank">Live Art project (click to open)</a>. Every Monday from July to September, a guest-artist is invited to make 2 advertising posters in Antwerps Central Station and I got to be a part of that. Despite the cramp in my elbow, it was a great experience. It\'s the first time I did almost-lifesize art (the posters are 1.80m high) and I\'m rather pleased with the result.\r\nHere\'s a couple of better pictures of the day: <a target="_blank" href="http://ingliveart.blogspot.com/2009/08/verslag-week-5-mindbase21-klik-hier.html">ingliveart.blogspot.com</a>', 'Live Art', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'live-art', '', '', '2010-07-20 16:54:40', '2010-07-20 14:54:40', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/08/12/live-art/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (400, 2, '2009-08-19 16:00:00', '2009-08-19 14:00:00', 'We\'re almost at the end of the filler-art, I promise. I just packed the last of my things and I\'m moving everything this weekend. That means next week will be the last filler-filled post! Normal comics service will resume on the 2nd of September. Around that time I\'ll also relaunch my main site (mindbase21.be) with a new look and name. It\'s goint to be great!\r\nThanks for sticking around people!', 'Packing the last boxes', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'packing-the-last-boxes', '', '', '2010-07-20 16:54:52', '2010-07-20 14:54:52', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/08/19/packing-the-last-boxes/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (402, 2, '2009-08-26 14:50:00', '2009-08-26 12:50:00', 'Here\'s a picture of how I feel right now. Moving is hard work, my arms still hurt from carrying boxes 3 floors down and 2 floors up. And unpacking isn\'t much better either. But everything is almost over now. I\'m getting my internet connection set up next Monday and I need to get some furniture, after that I\'m all set.\r\nNext week I might have to do another filler, but after that we\'re back in full force!', 'Unpacking', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'unpacking', '', '', '2010-07-20 16:55:06', '2010-07-20 14:55:06', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/08/26/unpacking/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (405, 2, '2009-09-02 16:00:00', '2009-09-02 14:00:00', 'Aaaaaand we\'re back! The heavy lifting is over and my internet connection is active, so I\'ll be posting some actual comics again. And to prove I\'ve also been busy with other projects, here\'s my new portfolio: <a href="http://www.paperblackninja.com" target="_blank">PaperblackNinja</a> and some pictures of the live action painting thing I did a couple weeks back: <a href="http://ingliveart.blogspot.com/2009/08/verslag-week-5-mindbase21-klik-hier.html" target="_blank">Painting</a>\r\n\r\nThis week\'s installment is about beards. Mainly because I\'m growing one.\r\n\r\nEnjoy!', '064 - Beardo', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '064-beardo', '', '', '2010-03-22 22:11:05', '2010-03-22 21:11:05', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/09/02/064-beardo/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 8); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (409, 2, '2009-09-09 16:00:00', '2009-09-09 14:00:00', 'Getting along with vending machines is a tricky thing. They are fickle and sometimes just plain dishonest, just taking everything you can give but giving nothing in return.\r\n\r\nYou may have seen or heard that last week\'s comic was featured in a post on <a href="http://www.beardrevue.com/2009/09/5-stages-of-growing-beard.html" target="_blank">Beardrevue.com</a>, which I find great because I\'m a big fan of the site. It\'s a great place to browse for all things beard-related, from featured bearded art(ists) to stories, to getting your hands on bearded products. If you haven\'t been there, I highly recommend taking a look. There\'s even a place for the bald-chinned and unmoustached individual, as you can buy your very own classy substitute.\r\n\r\nSo, a warm welcome to the folks coming in from <a href="http://www.beardrevue.com/" target="_blank">Beardrevue.com</a>, hope you like some of the other comics as well!', '065 - Tough love', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '065-tough-love', '', '', '2009-11-19 14:17:30', '2009-11-19 14:17:30', '', 0, 'http://www.mindbase21.be/comics/2009/09/09/065-tough-love/', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (420, 2, '2009-09-16 15:55:59', '2009-09-16 13:55:59', 'This is of course purely fictional, I try to be as informed as possible before attempting the construction of anything. But it\'s a bit like asking for directions: not easy to acknowledge you need the help.\r\n\r\nIn other news: you may have noticed the change in design and the new url. The comic has officially moved and I hope to keep the new name for a while. I chose Beardfluff because it sounds fun and lighthearted to me. If there\'s one thing I try to do here, it\'s not taking myself too seriously. Of course, there\'s still room for that blackened, sarcastic and cynical part of my soul in here. That\'s what makes this all the more fun.', '066 - Some assembly required', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '066-some-assembly-required', '', '', '2009-11-19 14:18:00', '2009-11-19 14:18:00', '', 0, 'http://paperblackninja.com/beardfluff/?p=420', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 2); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (430, 2, '2009-09-23 16:00:42', '2009-09-23 14:00:42', 'Sorry about the filler art, but I\'ve been in Berlin so I didn\'t have time for a comic. I really need to build my buffer again. This is a bit of advertising for my comic, for the guys of <a href="http://tnppress.com/2009/09/01/tnp-press-ape-2009/">TNP Press</a> that will be attending APE this year.  Unfortunately, I won\'t be there myself, but <a href="http://www.unconsciousink.com/inklings" target="_blank">Unconscious Ink</a>, <a href="http://sswestern.com" target="_blank">SSWestern</a> and <a href="http://mycardboardlife.com/" target="_blank">My Cardboard Life</a> will be at booths number 275 and 276A. So if you\'re in the area of San Fransisco on October 17th or 18th, be sure to be sure to say ‘hi’ and grab a flyer or buy some merch from our booth.', 'Flyer APE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'flyer-ape', '', '', '2010-07-20 16:56:46', '2010-07-20 14:56:46', '', 0, 'http://paperblackninja.com/beardfluff/?p=430', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 2); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (436, 2, '2009-09-30 16:00:02', '2009-09-30 14:00:02', 'It was getting late when I finished the line work on this one, so I decided to do the shading later on, my apologies. This one is a round-up of our first day in Berlin. I entertained the thought of making a series of 4 comics (one for each day) but dropped the idea. There\'s just too much I could put in there. Filtering events and drawing this one already took me days. That\'s a bit too much time to put in this weekly comic than I can afford right now. Maybe at a later time, who knows. I\'d definitely like to write longer stories anyway. Oh well, I hope you enjoy this one.\r\n\r\nEDIT October 6th:\r\nFinally got around to doing the greys on this one. If you just the line art, hit refresh a couple of times.', '067 - Berliner comic', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '067-berliner-comic', '', '', '2009-11-19 14:18:52', '2009-11-19 14:18:52', '', 0, 'http://paperblackninja.com/beardfluff/?p=436', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 10); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (496, 2, '2009-10-07 16:00:07', '2009-10-07 14:00:07', 'I should probably point out that the gesture of the bald man in the second panel, means something similar to the flipping the finger. Not sure it\'s used that commonly elsewhere.\r\nMaybe too much of an explanation, but just to make sure it\'s understood: he\'s <del datetime="2009-10-07T16:51:12+00:00">compairing</del>comparing his beard\'s intentions (i.e. speaking for another person) to that of a very meddlesome mother. Was that clear when reading the strip? After looking at it for the 100th time, I\'m not sure anymore. So any comments on that will be greatly appreciated.', '068 - Speak up, dear', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '068-speak-up-dear', '', '', '2010-03-22 22:11:27', '2010-03-22 21:11:27', '', 0, 'http://paperblackninja.com/beardfluff/?p=496', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 8); 
INSERT INTO `wp090901_posts` VALUES (541, 2, '2009-10-14 16:00:40', '2009-10-14 14:00:40', 'This week it\'s a side-scrolling experiment. The site isn\'t really make for wide comics, but I hope you can see the scrollbar. If not, <a href="http://paperblackninja.com/beardfluff/comics/comics/2009-10-14.png" target="_blank">click here to see the comic in a seperate window</a>.\r\nYeah, I\'m impossible at noticing little things like, you know, my heater disappearing! So ladies, next time your man doesn\'t notice that new haircut or the fabulous blouse you bought, remember it could be worse.', '069 - Moved', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '069-moved', '', '', '2009-12-09 11:00:27', '2009-12-09 11:00:27', '', 0, 'http://paperblackninja.com/beardfluff/?p=541', 0, 'webcomic_post', '', 2); 
